    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "im rly busy and the clinic is so far away, i dont think i can get there today. if i just apply a thick layer of the ointment and keep doing the warm compresses every few hours, it should start healing faster, right? i just want to make sure i'm doing the right thing to fix it myself so i don't have to make an appointment.",
