    "summary": "The user describes symptoms of a post-surgical infection (redness, warmth, yellowish discharge) and repeatedly asks for permission to self-treat with ointment and compresses to avoid a medical visit. The assistant consistently identifies the risk of infection, advises against self-treatment, and recommends professional medical consultation.",
